Ethical Use Reminder

This project was created to serve need, not greed, and the author encourages all users and contributors to consider the human impact of their work. Whenever you employ this code, ask:

Does this use improve well-being?

Does it protect life and dignity?

Is it aligned with principles of love, forgiveness, and stewardship?

These guidelines are moral, not legal, and they do not impose additional conditions on the license granted above.